1
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:10,759
What?

2
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,540
Don't dare to drink it?

3
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:18,329
If it were really poisoned,

4
00:02:18,640 --> 00:02:20,170
having drunk it for so long,

5
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,450
how could I not know?

6
00:02:22,640 --> 00:02:23,500
Your Highness.

7
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:25,500
Your Highness.

8
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:29,440
If

9
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:31,320
I drink it for you,

10
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:32,760
will that prove

11
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:34,290
that I didn't poison it?

12
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:01,360
Miss Anli,

13
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:04,060
I have drunk the medicine as you ordered.

14
00:03:04,440 --> 00:03:06,100
Does this prove my innocence?

15
00:03:06,160 --> 00:03:06,520
You!

16
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:11,100
I don't care what tricks you're playing.

17
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:13,160
If you dare to harm His Highness in the slightest,

18
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:14,420
I will never let you go.

19
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:18,880
I don't know where exactly

20
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:20,280
I have offended Miss Anli,

21
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,740
that you always target me.

22
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,280
Enough.

23
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:24,400
Miss Anli,

24
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,930
stop this nonsense.

25
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,300
Brother Yunchuan,

26
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:29,010
you'd rather believe a maid

27
00:03:29,079 --> 00:03:30,320
than believe me?

28
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:32,360
It's not that I don't want to believe you.

29
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,560
Seeing is believing.

30
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,520
And she has already drunk it.

31
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:36,130
Alright,

32
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:37,380
go back now.

33
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:40,800
Take care, Miss Anli.

34
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,640
In terms of looks,

35
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:22,880
or talent,

36
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:26,800
where am I inferior to that lowly maid?

37
00:04:28,520 --> 00:04:31,600
Why won't you even look at me properly?

38
00:04:32,960 --> 00:04:34,720
Even just once.

39
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:43,000
When have I, Bai Anli, ever suffered such humiliation?

40
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:50,440
Since you are so heartless,

41
00:04:51,159 --> 00:04:52,480
one day,

42
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:55,960
I will trample you all under my feet.

43
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,520
Why?

44
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:05,640
Why won't you ever

45
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:07,400
look at me properly?

46
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,480
Even just once.

47
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:11,600
Where did you get so angry, Miss?

48
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:13,080
Why are you in such a temper?

49
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:14,480
Should I invite Consort Yu

50
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,810
to seek justice for you?

51
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:20,880
About today's matter,

52
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:24,400
if you dare reveal a single word to her,

53
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:28,290
I won't let you off lightly.

54
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:30,620
Jing'er obeys.

55
00:05:40,159 --> 00:05:41,020
Your Highness.

56
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:42,060
Your Highness.

57
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,960
Don't bother me.

58
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:46,080
I haven't rested enough yet.

59
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:47,840
Miss Anli is here.

60
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,659
Princess Anli,

61
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:53,930
why are you here?

62
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,060
I came at a bad time.

63
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,240
I disturbed the Second Prince's rest.

64
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,000
Not at all.

65
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,940
You can come here anytime.

66
00:06:04,080 --> 00:06:04,940
Your Highness,

67
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:07,090
you must be tired from reading.

68
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,930
I happened to bring some snacks

69
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:11,400
to help you relax.

70
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:12,810
Alright,

71
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,250
then I must try some.

72
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:41,159
Your Highness, come and taste them.

73
00:06:41,159 --> 00:06:42,400
How is my cooking?

74
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:50,170
Your skills are no less than the palace chefs.

75
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:51,980
If Your Highness likes it,

76
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:55,159
I will make more and bring them to you.

77
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:03,740
You came today,

78
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:06,280
is there something you want to ask of me?

79
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:11,440
To tell the truth, Your Highness,

80
00:07:11,440 --> 00:07:12,960
I do have a favor to ask.

81
00:07:13,760 --> 00:07:15,360
I just arrived at the palace,

82
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:16,920
with no one to rely on.

83
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:19,130
The only one I could think of

84
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:22,040
is Your Highness.

85
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,640
Is someone bullying you?

86
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,640
I'll go teach them a lesson for you.

87
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:27,040
It's just a small matter.

88
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:29,360
Your Highness doesn't need to get involved personally.

89
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,200
I just need

90
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:32,520
two helpers.

91
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,330
Alright.

92
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:49,520
You tied me up without permission, Your Highness.

93
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:51,840
Aren't you afraid of Consort Yu's punishment?

94
00:07:51,840 --> 00:07:53,300
You are mistaken, Auntie.

95
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:54,600
I invited you here

96
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:55,960
just to have a cup of tea.

97
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:58,320
I didn't expect Tingfeng to misunderstand.

98
00:07:58,320 --> 00:07:59,980
Please don't take it to heart.

99
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:00,640
Tingfeng,

100
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,330
untie her immediately!

101
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:04,170
Yes, Your Highness.

102
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:20,480
Since it's a misunderstanding,

103
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:21,810
I will take my leave now.

104
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:22,680
No rush.

105
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,680
I actually have a few questions

106
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:25,720
for you.

107
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:28,260
As long as you answer truthfully,

108
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:30,200
I promise I won't make things difficult for you.

109
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:32,640
I rarely interact with you, Your Highness.

110
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:35,250
I'm afraid I cannot clear your doubts.

111
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:38,400
I'm just curious

112
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:40,840
why you appeared tonight at

113
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:42,440
Fengyao Palace.

114
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:47,600
The late Queen was kind and benevolent.

115
00:08:48,160 --> 00:08:50,160
I am just grateful for her kindness,

116
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,560
which is why I came to pay my respects

117
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:54,020
at Fengyao Palace on her death anniversary.

118
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:59,560
I heard you used to serve my mother.

119
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,880
You must have shared a deep bond.

120
00:09:03,560 --> 00:09:04,960
If my mother is in the netherworld

121
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:06,160
and knows about this,

122
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,560
she would surely be pleased.

123
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:09,890
Unfortunately,

124
00:09:10,040 --> 00:09:12,040
I never got the chance to see her again.

125
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:13,280
So I want to ask you

126
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,960
about some old matters concerning my mother.

127
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:18,600
I only served the late Queen for two years,

128
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:21,240
so I cannot answer your questions, Your Highness.

129
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,970
You are a smart person, Auntie.

130
00:09:23,520 --> 00:09:26,040
Were you present when my mother was giving birth?

131
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:26,800
Was her death

132
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,490
really an accident?

133
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:30,240
I wasn't the only one there.

134
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:32,000
Over a dozen people in the palace

135
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:34,200
were attending to her during the birth.

136
00:09:34,280 --> 00:09:36,440
You're asking me this so suddenly, Your Highness.

137
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,900
I don't know how to answer.

138
00:09:44,640 --> 00:09:46,170
Excuse me, is anyone there?

139
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,130
Is anyone there?

140
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:48,720
Coming!

141
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:51,480
Excuse me,

142
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,970
where is Lady Xue Le?

143
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:55,920
That's me.

144
00:09:56,400 --> 00:09:57,480
Consort Yu sent a message.

145
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:59,610
She needs you to go over for something.

146
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:01,040
Consort Yu?

147
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:04,410
Shouldn't Aunt Huixin be the one to invite me?

148
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:05,320
Please.

149
00:10:20,880 --> 00:10:21,740
Your Highness.

150
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,930
This Huixin is quite interesting.

151
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:25,360
She is very respectful to you

152
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,520
and answers every question,

153
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:28,320
but not a single word is the truth.

154
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,080
Your Highness,

155
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,940
why don't we make her suffer a bit?

156
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:32,720
Maybe then she will confess.

157
00:10:33,880 --> 00:10:35,480
She has been with Consort Yu for so long.

158
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:37,280
I suppose ordinary punishments

159
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:38,280
won't work on her.

160
00:10:39,040 --> 00:10:40,900
Besides, we have no evidence now.

161
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:42,160
If we really hurt her,

162
00:10:42,680 --> 00:10:44,680
I'm afraid it will only anger Consort Yu.

163
00:10:44,680 --> 00:10:46,400
It would be difficult to find the truth

164
00:10:46,400 --> 00:10:47,360
then.

165
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:51,160
Alright.

166
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:53,180
You should rest early too.

167
00:10:54,160 --> 00:10:55,020
Your Highness.

168
00:10:55,400 --> 00:10:57,600
Ling Xueyue hasn't come back yet.

169
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,960
It's so late, and she's not back yet.

170
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:04,800
Okay.

171
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,660
I'll go out and take a look.

172
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:08,640
Your Highness.

173
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:09,100
This...

174
00:11:14,800 --> 00:11:15,260
Xueyue,

175
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:16,640
I finally found you.

176
00:11:16,640 --> 00:11:17,770
I'm here to save you.

177
00:11:18,640 --> 00:11:19,440
First Prince.

178
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:21,560
How dare you.

179
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:23,580
You dare to take my people?

180
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:29,640
Your Highness,

181
00:11:29,640 --> 00:11:30,400
what happened?

182
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:31,600
Should we call a medical officer?

183
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:32,260
Not for now.

184
00:11:40,920 --> 00:11:41,720
You're awake.

185
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:42,960
Tingfeng,

186
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:44,300
pour a cup of water.

187
00:11:46,520 --> 00:11:47,560
How are you feeling?

188
00:11:47,560 --> 00:11:48,420
Your Highness.

189
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:53,570
Don't worry.

190
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:55,890
I had Chunlan change your clothes.

191
00:11:57,160 --> 00:11:58,620
Thank you, Your Highness.

192
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:01,000
Thank you.

193
00:12:07,480 --> 00:12:09,140
You were in danger right after

194
00:12:09,640 --> 00:12:10,770
we took Huixin away.

195
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:14,810
Could Consort Yu have noticed something?

196
00:12:15,040 --> 00:12:16,300
It can't be Consort Yu.

197
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:17,840
If it were her,

198
00:12:18,520 --> 00:12:19,980
I wouldn't have survived.

199
00:12:20,640 --> 00:12:21,800
But,

200
00:12:22,760 --> 00:12:24,020
other than Consort Yu,

201
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:26,060
who else would attack you?

202
00:12:27,880 --> 00:12:28,920
Could you have

203
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:30,410
offended someone else?

204
00:12:31,040 --> 00:12:33,480
I wasn't familiar with those two dark figures

205
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:34,410
who attacked me.

206
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:35,480
But

207
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:38,240
the voice of the person up close,

208
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:39,940
I definitely recognized.

209
00:12:40,280 --> 00:12:41,140
It was Bai Anli.

210
00:12:42,160 --> 00:12:43,240
Lady Anli

211
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:44,700
seems weak and gentle.

212
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:47,100
How could she be so malicious?

213
00:12:48,120 --> 00:12:48,840
Weakness

214
00:12:48,920 --> 00:12:50,080
is just her protective shell

215
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:51,480
to survive in the palace.

216
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:53,240
Her actions today

217
00:12:54,880 --> 00:12:56,880
were to make me leave Your Highness.

218
00:12:57,560 --> 00:12:58,960
Who does she think she is?

219
00:12:59,400 --> 00:13:01,080
How dare she meddle in Yuze Palace's affairs.

220
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:01,680
Forget it.

221
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:03,480
Today,

222
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:06,540
fortunately Your Highness arrived in time.

223
00:13:06,640 --> 00:13:07,960
I'm fine now, aren't I?

224
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:10,800
Business is more important right now.

225
00:13:10,800 --> 00:13:13,400
It's best we don't complicate things further.

226
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:17,400
It's my fault for involving you.

227
00:13:19,160 --> 00:13:19,640
Right,

228
00:13:20,240 --> 00:13:21,640
did Huixin say anything?

229
00:13:23,880 --> 00:13:24,740
You were right.

230
00:13:25,600 --> 00:13:27,260
Consort Yu trusts her so much.

231
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:29,400
She isn't that easy to deal with.

232
00:13:31,520 --> 00:13:32,120
Then,

233
00:13:32,680 --> 00:13:34,210
is she still in Yuze Palace?

234
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:36,930
She is locked in the small room.

235
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:37,800
By the way.

236
00:13:37,800 --> 00:13:38,600
This Huixin

237
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:39,860
is quite interesting.

238
00:13:39,880 --> 00:13:41,480
She neither eats nor drinks,

239
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:42,560
and doesn't say anything.

240
00:13:42,560 --> 00:13:44,220
She just stays there quietly.

241
00:13:44,800 --> 00:13:46,880
Since we invited her to Yuze Palace,

242
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:49,930
we might as well treat her well.

243
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:57,660
What are you doing?

244
00:14:01,560 --> 00:14:02,720
His Highness ordered.

245
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:04,840
Aunt Huixin is Concubine Yu's person,

246
00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:06,240
so we cannot neglect her.

247
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:07,320
Tell His Highness

248
00:14:07,400 --> 00:14:08,730
not to waste his effort.

249
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:10,260
I don't know anything.

250
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:13,900
If you want to stay here permanently,

251
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:15,720
our Yuze Palace can afford it.

252
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:17,000
You!

253
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:26,700
I thought about it.

254
00:14:27,640 --> 00:14:30,200
Huixin is so loyal to Concubine Yu,

255
00:14:30,880 --> 00:14:32,540
there might be other reasons.

256
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:35,120
You mean

257
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:38,440
Concubine Yu has a way to control Huixin?
